### Feature Flags in Deployments

Integrate feature flag services (LaunchDarkly, Unleash) into your application to decouple deployment from feature release. This allows deploying code to production disabled, then gradually enabling it for user segments without redeploying.

```typescript
const isNewUIEnabled = await featureFlags.isEnabled(
  'new-ui-v2',
  { userId: user.id, country: user.country }
);

if (isNewUIEnabled) {
  return renderNewUI();
} else {
  return renderLegacyUI();
}
```

**Common interview trap:** Implementing flags only in frontend; backend logic changes must also be feature-flagged for true safety.

